config MIDI
	bool "Minimal SMF MIDI parser and polyphonic DDS synthesizer"
	help
	  Enable the in-tree MIDI library. Parses Standard MIDI Files (Format 0
	  and 1) from a raw byte array and synthesizes polyphonic sine-wave audio
	  as int16_t PCM with no dynamic memory allocation. Requires math.h
	  (sinf, powf) — enable CONFIG_FPU for hardware acceleration.
